nhc_headline: ...BARBARA EXPECTED TO BECOME A REMNANT LOW SOON...
summary: ...BARBARA EXPECTED TO BECOME A REMNANT LOW SOON... As of 2:00 PM MST Tue Jun 10 the center of Barbara was located near 20.9, -108.1 with movement N at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
